So as you've probably gathered,
people who drive electric cars,

00:18:57.730 --> 00:18:58.970
they love their cars.

00:18:58.970 --> 00:19:03.500
They become EV-angelists,
sorry for the pun.

00:19:03.500 --> 00:19:06.560
And I've had the good
fortune of meeting

00:19:06.560 --> 00:19:10.510
Brian who is a Sierra Club
supporter and member and EV

00:19:10.510 --> 00:19:11.820
driver.

00:19:11.820 --> 00:19:15.050
And I've had the
fortune of meeting lots,

00:19:15.050 --> 00:19:16.650
and lots, and lots
of very excited

00:19:16.650 --> 00:19:19.750
enthusiastic electric car
drivers around the country.

00:19:19.750 --> 00:19:22.350
And since Brian is
