00:19:22.350 --> 00:19:24.750
we thought it would be great
if he came up and shared

00:19:24.750 --> 00:19:26.290
a little bit about
his experience

00:19:26.290 --> 00:19:27.220
with his Nissan Leaf.

00:19:27.220 --> 00:19:29.610
So why doesn't
Brian come up, talk

00:19:29.610 --> 00:19:31.860
a little bit about his
