is less polluting.

00:43:20.790 --> 00:43:23.220
In other ways, there are
significant environmental

00:43:23.220 --> 00:43:23.720
costs.

00:43:23.720 --> 00:43:29.120
Sometimes the land that
that you have to develop

00:43:29.120 --> 00:43:32.420
and the water that you have to
pollute because of the ethanol

00:43:32.420 --> 00:43:36.500
production is going to have a
very heavy environmental cost.

00:43:36.500 --> 00:43:39.590
So I would say overall, the
